column1: Daily Weather Observations for Murrurundi, New South Wales for March 2021
Prepared at 16:01 UTC on Thursday  7 October 2021   IDCJDW2196.202103
Observations for Murrurundi are now taken at a site in Haydon Street, replacing those from the Post Office.
Temperature, humidity, wind, cloud and rainfall observations are from Murrurundi (Haydon Street) {station 061431}
Pressure observations are from Murrurundi Gap AWS {station 061392}
